Your Brand,
Your Fragance
settings.text: It’s more than just diffusing a fragrance in a showroom or lobby — it’s the science of combining your brand identity, message, and the values of your target audience. The Emotional
Connection
settings.text: With over 1,00 odor receptors in our brains, we can easily identify over 10,000 individual scents. settings.title: Our story
settings.text: From the ingredients found in our Aroma Oils to the technology that drives our diffusers, we consider every element of our fragrance experience to ensure we’re staying true to our ethical and quality commitments.
We work with the world’s top luxury retail and hospitality companies to develop custom fragrances for their spaces.

settings.title:
APPLE STORE

THE GROVE
settings.text: We developed a custom fragrance for the launch of Apple’s new location at The Grove in Los Angeles. Combining the iconic company’s clean, streamlined aesthetic and welcoming atmosphere, we worked to develop a bright, inviting fragrance that energized their employees and excited customers.

settings.title: Our Story
settings.text: AromaTechTM is a company dedicated to enhancing environments through fragrance innovation. Since 2009, we have been committed to providing the highest-quality fragrances for spaces using safe, sustainable ingredients delivered through the most powerful nebulizing technology available.

settings.title: Our Ingredients Philosophy
settings.text: In order to receive their full sensory benefits, we only use 100% pure essential oils in our fragrance blends and ensure they are sustainable, safe, and stable. Our Aroma Oils are free from parabens, sulfates, glycols, petrochemicals, synthetic colours, and other additives, and we’re compliant with all industry inhalation and diffusion rates to ensure your comfort and safety when diffusing at home.

settings.title: Our Innovative Technology
settings.text: Each of our fragrance nebulizers uses patented cold-air diffusion technology to release nanoparticles into the air that leave behind no residue. This technology preserves the integrity of our Aroma Oils to deliver pristine, evenly distributed fragrance without using heat or diluting the oils in water or alcohol.

settings.title: Do you have a subscription service?
settings.a: Each of our fragrance nebulizers uses patented cold-air diffusion technology to release nanoparticles into the air that leave behind no residue. Rather than diluting with water and heat, AromaTech’s scent diffusers use a combination of 100% essential oils and filtered air from your space. This technology preserves the integrity of our Aroma Oils to deliver pristine, evenly distributed fragrance without using heat or diluting the oils in water or alcohol.

settings.title: Do you have instructional videos?
settings.a: No water is needed. Our diffuser will transform pure aroma oil into dry air, preserving all the natural benefits. No humidity or residue will be produced.

settings.title: What is a nebulizing diffuser?
settings.a:
The safest and cleanest way to diffuse your 100% essential oils

Preservation of maximum essential oil therapeutic properties

Longer lasting and consistent aromas

Uses less oil than traditional diffusers.

settings.title: No water is needed?

settings.producttxt: In a cafe on the corner of 7th and West 35th, I waited for my coffee and read the business section in the Times. It was a brisk and refreshing morning. The sunlight began to shine through busy streets as the smell of fresh brewed coffee and espresso wafted across the shop. I reached for my to-go cup and freshly baked chocolate croissant to begin my day. The aroma of roasted caramelized nuts from a street vendor prolonged in the morning air as I watched the locals briskly walk towards the gleaming towers of downtown. Chocolatey notes of cream and cocoa drifted from my coffee as I stirred in a treat of Bailey’s and faded into the daily hustle of NYC.

The radiating heat of the fireplace warmed my body as I rested on a vintage wingback leather chair. I watched the dry wood slowly transform to warm ambers as the fire danced and glistened; crackling and popping with every move. I brought the glass of brandy closer to my nose to smell the intoxicating aromas. My body nourished from a delicious supper, the air was still intimate of plum and fruit aroma. I felt a sense of serenity as the quiet evening continued in the British country home. The vanilla-laced smoke of a fine cigar slowly burned as I took pleasure from my comforts.
settings.producttxtk: Plum Brandy • Leather • Tobacco • Cedar • Vanilla • Tolu Balsam

settings.producttxt: Fixated on the pulsing bass vibrating the concrete beneath my feet. My focus interrupted by the gleaming headlights of luxury cars pulling up to the scene. Friends and colleagues full of laughter and excitement approached the valet, handing off the keys and disappearing into the night club. As they entered the aroma of Russian leather and warm amber wafted into the streets. I was greeted by a beautiful hostess who prompted me towards the entrance with a smile. The contrast of antique building exterior transitioned into a luxurious interior full of individual extravagances and wealth. The passionate and lustful scent of champagne corks popping filled the room. The comforting aroma of black tea brewing in the distance drifted across the air. A night to remember, lavishment and lust.
settings.producttxtk: Champagne • Russian Black Tea • Incense • Birch Leather • Amber

settings.producttxt: Escaping the scorching desert heat, I found myself wandering down the glimmering hallways of the world's grandest shopping center. I was immediately refreshed by the cool indoor atmosphere and paused to take a deep breath. The aroma of Bakhoor incense lingered in the air as I admired the magnificent building surrounding me. A state of the art, extravagant and exotic city; preserving distinctive traditions while welcoming the new. The fragrance of jammy red roses wafted over me as I passed by elegant Arabic women dressed in black abayas. Their husbands contrasting in white dishdashas. The scent of their dark wood smoking oudhs drifted into the atmosphere. Admiration for their luxurious lifestyle instilled in my mind as I continued exploring the city.

A large crowd of people rushed past me up the stairs, I followed them out of the underground train station and found myself breathing the crisp Spring air. A beautiful contrast, I was lost in translation between the vibrant city and the calming oriental gardens surrounding me. A culture that is so minimal, yet elegantly bursting with life. I was in a meditative state. The breeze carried the scent of sakura cherry blossoms and citrus notes. It stirred through the leaves of the Hinoki Trees and down the glistening streets. In the distance, I observed Sadouka women taking practice in a traditional tea ceremony. The aroma of fine matcha powder whisked with steaming hot water, filling me with tranquility and relaxation.
settings.producttxtk: Yuzu • Wasabi • Cherry Blossom • Hinoki Wood • Green Tea

settings.sub_main_heading: An Idea Transformed Into A Work Of Art
settings.sub_main_text: We took the concept of transporting you to a place through a distinctive scent and combined it with a journey around the world.
settings.thirdsectiontitlesub: We are thrilled to share with you this luxurious collection of fragrances. Experience the world with us.
settings.secondsectiontitle: The Nose Behind It All: Meet Ryan
settings.secondsectiontxt: When I was a young boy I remember my Grandfather getting ready early every morning for work. Shaving foam, Brylcreem, and splash on cologne in the form of Dior Eau Sauvage. Smelling those grooming items almost over 30 years later will bring me right back to standing outside the bathroom doorway watching him with love and wonder while he completed his daily routine. This was my earliest memory of falling in love with fragrances.
